description: Fabulous 1 bedroom at the St. Regis! The only 1 BR available with ACTUAL water views! Floor to ceiling windows provide sweeping views of the harbor, as well as the action and lights of the city! Windows flood the space with light. Custom built-ins include a living room wall unit, foyer armoire with hidden shoe storage, and a large kitchen island. Generous bedroom with great city views, has WI closet and a second closet. A spa bath with radiant floor heat, coat closet, and a laundry room completes the unit. Building features include the expansive amenity level with swimming pool, steam, sauna, hot tub, spa, & fitness center. A private resident lounge and meeting rooms with glorious harbor views, golf simulator, and two hospitality suites for overnight guests. 24-hour concierge, doorman & butler service and Savr restaurant with exclusive residents' entrance complete the features of this luxury residence. Garage parking available to rent. Enjoy life in the heart of the Seaport!
